name: Dotonbori
description:
The Dotonbori neighbourhood in Osaka, Japan. 

Exploring the streets and alleys of this district, one immediately calls to mind all things cyberpunk. Indeed, this neighbourhood was one of the inspirations for the overall aesthetic of Blade Runner.

Fully alive at night, Dotonbori is home to hundreds of incredible street stalls, bars, and restaurants. A must-experience for any visitor to Japan.
